public class ModuleUsageNode

The usage details of an Module from Topology Manager that contains Business Objects (View Objects) that may participate in Social Network integration via the Social Network Setups page Objects tree-table.

setDisclosed

public void setDisclosed(java.lang.Boolean disclosed)
Determine if the UI should show this item as being open(disclosed). Since this Module Usage is responsible for triggering the loading of the structure of the child view objects upon first disclosure then this method will trigger that loading the first time this method is called.

Specified by:

fullyLoadViewObjectsFromPreLoad

public void fullyLoadViewObjectsFromPreLoad(SocialNetworkSendEventListener sendListener)
Take the list of pre-loaded view objects and fully load each one. After this method has completed all children will be fully functional and the pre-load structure will be null.

Parameters:
sendListener - the listener monitor the view objects being loaded. Null is valid.

addPreLoadedViewObjectUsageNode

public void addPreLoadedViewObjectUsageNode(ViewObjectUsageNode voUsageNode,
                                            ViewObjectNodeStructure voNode)
Register a View Object Usage and Node as being in the pre-loaded state. This will allow the tree structure to be built successfully without having the structure objects fully loaded which will happen on first disclosure of this module.
